!! Text Formatting

!!! Basic Formatting
This is ''bold text'' in a sentence.
This is //italic text// in a sentence.
This is __underlined text__ in a sentence.
This is ~~strikethrough text~~ in a sentence.
This is ^^superscript^^ in a sentence.
This is ,,subscript,, in a sentence.
This is `inline code` in a sentence.

!!! Nested Formatting
This is ''bold with //italic// inside''.
This is //italic with ''bold'' inside//.
This is ''bold with __underline__ inside''.
This is __underline with ~~strikethrough~~ inside__.
This is ''//bold italic//'' together.
This is //''italic bold''// together.
This is ''__bold underline__'' together.
This is ~~//strikethrough italic//~~ together.
This is ''//~~bold italic strikethrough~~//'' all three.
This is ^^super with ''bold'' inside^^ works.
This is ,,sub with //italic// inside,, works.

!!! Deep Nesting
''Bold with //italic with __underline with ~~strike with `code`~~__//''.
//Italic ''bold __underline ~~strike~~__''//.

!!! Formatting at Boundaries
''bold at start'' of line.
End of line is ''bold''
''entire line is bold''
//italic at start// of line.
End of line is //italic//
//entire line is italic//
__underline at start__ of line.
~~strikethrough at start~~ of line.

!!! Edge Cases for Formatting
Single 'apostrophe' should not be bold.
Double ''apostrophes'' are bold.
Three '''apostrophes''' test.
Four ''''apostrophes'''' test.
//italic with space before closing //
''bold with space before closing ''
// italic at start//
''bold''immediate text after
//italic//immediate text after
Text''bold''text without spaces.
Text//italic//text without spaces.
''bold'' ''another bold'' multiple on line.
//italic// //another italic// multiple on line.

!!! Unclosed Formatting (graceful handling)
Unclosed ''bold without closing
Unclosed //italic without closing
Unclosed __underline without closing
Unclosed ~~strikethrough without closing
Unclosed ^^superscript without closing
Unclosed ,,subscript without closing

!!! Code Formatting
Inline `code with spaces` works.
`code at start` of line.
End with `code`
Multiple `code` blocks `in one` line `here`.
`code with ''bold'' inside` should show as code only.
`code with special <chars> & "quotes"`
Empty `` backticks.
`code with
newline` should not work across lines.
Unclosed `code without closing

!!! Mixed Formatting with Links
''Bold with [[WikiLink]] inside''.
//Italic with {{transclusion}} inside//.
__Underline with <<simpleInlineMacro>> inside__.
''//Bold italic with [[Link|Target]]//''.

