!! Summary

This comprehensive test covers:

!!! Pragma Types
* `\define` - macro definitions (inline and multi-line)
* `\procedure` - procedure definitions
* `\function` - function definitions
* `\widget` - custom widget definitions
* `\parameters` - default parameters
* `\import` - importing macros
* `\rules` - parser rule control
* `\whitespace` - whitespace handling

!!! Block Elements
* Headings (all 6 levels with formatting)
* Lists (bullet, numbered, definition, mixed, quoted)
* Block quotes (with classes, citations, nested content)
* Tables (all features including merging, captions, classes)
* Code blocks (all languages)
* Typed blocks
* Horizontal rules

!!! Inline Elements
* Text formatting (bold, italic, underline, strikethrough, super/subscript, code)
* Links (wiki, external, image, CamelCase, system, auto-URL)
* Transclusions (simple, field, index, filtered, with template)
* Macros (simple, parameterized, nested)
* Entities and escapes
* Dashes
* Highlighting/styled text

!!! Widgets
* All common widgets with various attribute types
* Self-closing vs container
* Namespaced widgets
* Action widgets
* Slot and fill widgets

!!! HTML
* All common elements
* HTML5 semantic elements
* SVG
* Form elements
* Self-closing/void elements

!!! Conditionals
* `<%if%>`, `<%else%>`, `<%elseif%>`, `<%endif%>`
* Nested conditionals

!!! Filters
* All operator categories
* Run prefixes
* Variable, text, and macro references

!!! Attributes
* String (regular and triple-quoted)
* Indirect (transclusion)
* Macro
* Filter
* Substituted
* Boolean

!!! Edge Cases
* Empty elements
* Unclosed elements
* Deep nesting
* Unicode
* Special characters
* Long lines
* Whitespace sensitivity

